# Keep a very small public surface by default.
# If you intentionally want to track a file matched below,
# either add a negation rule here or use `git add -f`.

# OS
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.code-workspace

# Temporary / backup files
~$*
*.tmp
*.bak
*.old
*.orig
*.rej

# Logs / generated measurement files
DATELOG*.TXT
DATELOG*.txt
*.log
*.out

# Archives and packages
*.7z
*.zip
*.rar
*.tar
*.gz
*.bz2
*.xz

# Office and document files
*.pdf
*.doc
*.docx
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.xlsm
*.ppt
*.pptx

# Images / video / audio
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.bmp
*.tif
*.tiff
*.heic
*.webp
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.wmv
*.mkv
*.webm
*.mp3
*.wav

# CAD / CAM / analysis artifacts
*.SLDPRT
*.SLDASM
*.SLDDRW
*.sldprt
*.sldasm
*.slddrw
*.sldprt~
*.sldasm~
*.slddrw~
*.CWR
*.cwr
*.DXF
*.dxf
*.STL
*.stl
*.STEP
*.step
*.STP
*.stp
*.IGS
*.igs
*.IGES
*.iges
swxJRNL.swj

# Executables / binary tools
*.exe
*.dll
*.msi

# High-risk names often tied to personal or submission data
*学生証*
*名簿*
*申請書*
*提出用*
*提出書類*
*誓約書*
*承諾書*
*保険*
*連絡先*

# Existing large archival directories in this repository
/EcoRun ~2021/
/Ecorun 2022/
/Ene-1 ~2021/
/mosaic/
/エコランまとめ/
/引継ぎ資料まとめ秋元/

# Core repo files to keep trackable
!.gitignore
!README.md
!docs/
!docs/images/
!docs/images/**
